'''愛國者運動'''（{{lang-en|'''Patriot movement'''}}）是一項[[美國|美國]]的[[社會運動|社會運動]]。由當地民眾自發組成的{{link-en|民兵組織|Militia organizations in the United States}}從事，他們主張[[美國保守主義|保守]]、獨立<ref name=Right-wing>[https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=S9UpAAAAIBAJ&sjid=T88EAAAAIBAJ&pg=3212,1858703  Right-wing Counterculture Uses Waco as Rallying Cry] {{Wayback|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=S9UpAAAAIBAJ&sjid=T88EAAAAIBAJ&pg=3212,1858703 |date=20210417225230 }}| Herald-Journal 24 April 1995</ref>。成員包括{{link-en|稅務抗議者|Tax protester}}、[[主權公民運動者|主權公民運動者]]、[[聖經啟示文學|啟示錄末日論者]]、[[生存主義|極端生存主義者]]、[[極右派|極右派]][[自由意志主義|自由意志主義者]]、[[反猶太主義|反猶太主義者]]及其他組合，主要由前[[美軍|軍方]]、[[美國警察|警方]]領導<ref name=Abanes>[http://www.asa3.org/ASA/PSCF/1997/PSCF6-97Feucht.html AMERICAN MILITIAS: Rebellion, Racism & Religion] {{Wayback|url=http://www.asa3.org/ASA/PSCF/1997/PSCF6-97Feucht.html |date=20150923174413 }} by Richard Abanes, review by Dennis L. Feucht in ''American Scientific Affiliation''.</ref>。

許多領導者是美國[[特種部隊|特種部隊]]的退役人員，組織上大都模仿[[軍事組織|軍隊編制]]，裝備齊全，經常購置槍枝彈藥、進行軍事訓練和實戰演習，隨時準備進行戰鬥。他們認為現在的[[美國聯邦政府|美國聯邦政府]]正不斷侵犯他們的權利（包括民選政府官員，官僚機構以及一些政府外的特殊利益集團，以違憲的手段非法積累權力），所以不得不進行戰鬥<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20090401210954/http://www.americanpatriotmovement.com/ John Wallace, American Patriot Movement]</ref>。他們自稱是真正的愛國者，要進行一場反對聯邦政府[[專制主義|專制統治]]的[[革命|革命]]，恢復[[民主|民主]]、自由的美國傳統。他們要求聯邦政府堅持《[[美國憲法|美國憲法]]》，停止有計劃的濫用[[地皮|土地權]]、[[美國槍支政策|槍枝權]]、[[言論自由|言論自由]]和其他自由<ref name="WaPoSullivan">{{cite web|language=en|last1=Sullivan|first1=Kevin|title=Primed to Fight The Government|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/sf/national/2016/05/21/armed-with-guns-and-constitutions-the-patriot-movement-sees-america-under-threat/|website=[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]|date=2016-05-21|accessdate=2017-03-23|archive-date=2017-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170319233355/http://www.washingtonpost.com/sf/national/2016/05/21/armed-with-guns-and-constitutions-the-patriot-movement-sees-america-under-threat/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。記者和研究人員通常會將愛國者運動與右派民兵運動聯繫起來<ref>{{cite web|language=en|url=https://books.google.com/books?hl=en&lr=&id=Oceewj5YQkQC&oi=fnd&pg=PA63&dq=patriot%20movement&ots=QfBFdCL3bi&sig=EupwtMNl1vqEXxH-3GjpNyfMuiQ#v=onepage&q=patriot%20movement&f=false|title=The Age of Anxiety: Conspiracy Theory and the Human Sciences|first1=Jane|last1=Parish|first2=Martin|last2=Parker|date=2001-12-03|publisher=Wiley|via=Google Books|accessdate=2017-03-23|archive-date=2017-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170323065009/https://books.google.com/books?hl=en&lr=&id=Oceewj5YQkQC&oi=fnd&pg=PA63&dq=patriot%20movement&ots=QfBFdCL3bi&sig=EupwtMNl1vqEXxH-3GjpNyfMuiQ#v=onepage&q=patriot%20movement&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>，因為該運動有一些非法、暴力的行為，甚至和政府單位發生[[武裝衝突|武裝衝突]]<ref name=Right-wing>[https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=S9UpAAAAIBAJ&sjid=T88EAAAAIBAJ&pg=3212,1858703  Right-wing Counterculture Uses Waco as Rallying Cry]| Herald-Journal 24 April 1995</ref><ref name=autogenerated5>[http://www.salon.com/books/int/2002/01/17/hamm/print.html Salon.com Books | America's homegrown terrorists] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100130040611/http://www.salon.com/books/int/2002/01/17/hamm/print.html |date=2010-01-30 }}</ref><ref name=autogenerated2>{{cite news | language=en | url=https://www.nytimes.com/1996/06/23/us/ohio-case-typifies-the-tensions-between-militia-groups-and-law.html | work=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]] | title=Ohio Case Typifies the Tensions Between Militia Groups and Law | first=Michael | last=Winerip | date=1996-06-23 | accessdate=2017-03-23 | archive-date=2017-08-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170816015941/http://www.nytimes.com/1996/06/23/us/ohio-case-typifies-the-tensions-between-militia-groups-and-law.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。美國執法機構認為他們是危險、充滿妄想、有時是暴力的組織<ref name="WaPoSullivan"/>。

震驚或啟發愛國者運動的美國重大事件包括1992年[[紅寶石山脊|紅寶石山脊事件]]、1993年[[韋科慘案|韋科慘案]]和[[1996年夏季奧林匹克運動會|1996年夏季奧林匹克運動會]]。2008年[[巴拉克·歐巴馬|巴拉克·歐巴馬]]當選[[美國總統|美國總統]]後，愛國者運動的規模和人數急劇增加<ref name=npr>[http://www.npr.org/blogs/thetwo-way/2012/03/08/148217754/report-explosive-growth-of-patriot-movement-and-militias-continues Report: 'Explosive' Growth Of 'Patriot Movement' And Militias Continues] {{Wayback|url=http://www.npr.org/blogs/thetwo-way/2012/03/08/148217754/report-explosive-growth-of-patriot-movement-and-militias-continues |date=20141205103450 }} by Mark Memmott npr.org 13 March 2012</ref>。導致該運動擴大的其他因素包括[[社会化媒体|社群媒體]]的興起、[[全球主義|全球主義]]的興起、[[經濟大衰退|經濟大衰退]]及其後果、愛國者運動的[[白人優越主義|白人優越主義]]分支，以及美國的[[多元文化主義|種族多樣性]]增加<ref name="Public Eye">{{cite web|language=en|url=http://www.publiceye.org/right_wing_populism/patriot/index.html|title=PublicEye.org - The Website of Political Research Associates|publisher=Public Eye|accessdate=2017-03-23|archive-date=2016-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161201070516/http://www.publiceye.org/right_wing_populism/patriot/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該運動的象徵物包括[[美國革命|美國革命]]、[[分鐘人|殖民地義勇兵]]、{{link-en|貝特西·羅斯旗|Betsy Ross flag}}、[[山姆大叔|山姆大叔]]和《{{link-en|76精神|Archibald_Willard#The_Spirit_of_.2776}}》<ref>{{cite web|language=en|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2016/09/15/does-americas-first-flag-symbolize-exclusion-and-hate-like-this-mich-school-superintendent-said/?utm_term=.7e3a72e28c1f|title=Does America’s first flag symbolize ‘exclusion and hate,’ as this Mich. school superintendent said?|publisher=華盛頓郵報|date=2016-09-15|accessdate=2017-03-23|archive-date=2019-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190918205300/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2016/09/15/does-americas-first-flag-symbolize-exclusion-and-hate-like-this-mich-school-superintendent-said/?utm_term=.7e3a72e28c1f}}</ref>。

== 立場 ==
與愛國者運動對立的包括[[聯邦調查局|聯邦調查局]]、[[反誹謗聯盟|反誹謗聯盟]]、[[南方貧困法律中心|南方貧困法律中心]]、美國聯邦政府的官員和執法人員、猶太機構、墮胎提供者、政治候選人的支持者、環保活動家、[[同性戀|同性戀]]權益組織者等<ref name="Public Eye"/>。愛國者運動常被對立的一方形容為[[種族主義|種族主義者]]、[[極端主義|極端主義者]]、[[反猶太主義|反猶太主義者]]和暴力群體<ref name="splc1">{{cite web|language=en|url=https://www.splcenter.org/hatewatch/2015/04/16/key-events-and-crimes-patriot-movement|title=Key Events and Crimes of the Patriot Movement|website=SPLCenter.org|date=2015-04-15|access-date=2017-02-23|archive-date=2017-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170223103050/https://www.splcenter.org/hatewatch/2015/04/16/key-events-and-crimes-patriot-movement|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="splc2">{{cite web|language=en|url=https://www.splcenter.org/fighting-hate/intelligence-report/2015/patriot-movement-timeline|title=THE 'PATRIOT' MOVEMENT TIMELINE|website=SPLCenter.org|access-date=2017-02-23|archive-date=2017-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170222080716/https://www.splcenter.org/fighting-hate/intelligence-report/2015/patriot-movement-timeline|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="adl">{{cite web|language=en|url=http://www.adl.org/combating-hate/domestic-extremism-terrorism/c/the-oath-keepers.html#.WK-36vkrJhE|title=The Oath Keepers: Anti-Government Extremists Recruiting Military and Police|website=ADL.org|date=2015-09-16|access-date=2017-02-23|archive-date=2017-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170117150516/http://www.adl.org/combating-hate/domestic-extremism-terrorism/c/the-oath-keepers.html#.WK-36vkrJhE|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="fbi">{{cite web|language=en|url=https://www.fbi.gov/file-repository/stats-services-publications-terror_96.pdf/view|title=Terrorism in the United States 1996|website=FBi.gov|access-date=2017-02-23|archive-date=2017-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170224132035/https://www.fbi.gov/file-repository/stats-services-publications-terror_96.pdf/view|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

外界對愛國者運動的描述包括：
*一個多元化的社會運動，其共同點是對美國聯邦政府越來越高漲的不滿和異議，主張使用[[武裝力量|武裝力量]]捍衛自己的權利和意願，並且相信[[末世論|末世論]]和[[陰謀論|陰謀論]]<ref name=Abanes/>。
*以自由意志主義者、[[舊保守主義|舊保守主義者]]、{{link-en|古自由意志主義者|Paleolibertarianism}}、{{link-en|反對移民者|Opposition to immigration}}的[[民兵|武裝民兵]]組成，主張廢除[[聯邦儲備系統|聯邦儲備系統]]、縮小聯邦政府職權<ref>[https://www.nytimes.com/2010/02/16/us/politics/16teaparty.html?pagewanted=all Tea Party Lights Fuse for Rebellion on Right] {{Wayback|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2010/02/16/us/politics/16teaparty.html?pagewanted=all |date=20170816191043 }} By DAVID BARSTOW| nyt.com 15 February 2010</ref>。
*主張維護《美國憲法》，特別是《[[美國憲法第二修正案|美國憲法第二條修正案]]》與《[[美利堅合眾國憲法第十四條修正案|美國憲法第十四條修正案]]》<ref name=autogenerated6>[https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=7KgsAAAAIBAJ&sjid=BxUEAAAAIBAJ&pg=2272,4215878 Patriot Movement is Alive and Well in the US] {{Wayback|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=7KgsAAAAIBAJ&sjid=BxUEAAAAIBAJ&pg=2272,4215878 |date=20210417225226 }} Los Angeles Daily News 26 December 1994 |(Wilmington NC, ''Star-News'' Google News Archive Search</ref>，也因此一些成員拒絕繳納[[所得稅|所得稅]]<ref name=autogenerated6 />。

愛國者運動與以下觀點有關：
*支持準軍事民兵運動，如{{link-en|密歇根州民兵隊|Michigan Militia}}<ref name=Right-wing />。
*宗教觀點集中於探討[[時間終結|時間終結]]的跡象<ref name=Right-wing/>。
*對[[大規模監控|大規模監控]]的抗議<ref name=autogenerated6 />。

